labels.name: triaged

items.body:
Try if our chrono job also works for tests from other repo.

https://app.circleci.com/jobs/github/pytorch/pytorch/4693216

The failure is due to torchvision dataset downloads from `http://yann.lecun.com/exdb/mnist/`. We can reenable this after torchvision dataset is switched to S3 mirror.
